# DXVK-macOS (Gcenx async repack) — a MoltenVK-tuned DXVK that renders D3D10/11
# on Apple Silicon where stock upstream DXVK can't (stock DXVK 2.x needs Vulkan
# 1.3 + geometry/tessellation shaders Apple GPUs lack; this 1.10.3-based build
# targets Vulkan 1.1 and relaxes those requirements). zlib-licensed, redistributable.
# Ships d3d11.dll + d3d10core.dll (paired with wine's builtin dxgi). Downloaded +
# extracted at build time (not committed).
